    <id>http://www.shiptux.cn/2018/04/21/my-ownlcoud/</id>
    <published>2018-04-21T05:56:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-04-21T05:55:51.218Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>当我打算尝试安装 <code>nextcloud</code> 的时候我的闲置主机网络出现了问题</p><p><img src="/img/2018/04/21/error.png" alt="error"></p><p>系统使用的是 <code>Fedora Server</code> ，我求助了 <code>FZUG -Fedora</code> 中文用户组，他们在我上次的投稿中给了我很多实用的建</p><p>议</p><p>经过 <code>Fedora Zhongwen User Group</code> 的 <code>Zamir SUN</code> 和 <code>Alick Zhao</code> 的帮助下解决了问题</p><p>我的一些不好的操作习惯给我引来了麻烦–我使用命令行配置了静态 IP 但是我并没有禁用 <code>Network Manager</code> </p><p><code>nmcli</code> 是命令行下的配置工具</p><p><code>nmtui</code> 是 <code>text-based-ui</code> 下的配置工具 </p><p>不使用的话建议禁用或在配置文件中加入 NM-CONTROLLED=no</p><p>##安装NextCloud</p><ol><li><p>更新软件包</p><p><code> dnf update </code></p></li><li><p>安装nextcloud</p><p><code> dnf install -y nextcloud-nginx.noarch nextcloud.noarch </code></p></li><li><p>安装数据库 mariadb</p><p><code> dnf install -y mariadb mariadb-server </code></p></li><li><p>启动</p><p><code> systemctl start nginx php-fpm mariadb </code></p></li><li><p>开机默认启动</p><p><code> systemctl enable nginx php-fpm mariadb </code></p></li></ol><p>##配置MariaDB</p><ol><li><p>简单配置</p><p><code> mysql_secure_installation </code></p></li><li><p>设置密码 </p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">Set</span> root <span class="keyword">password</span>? [Y/n] &lt;– 是否设置root用户密码，输入y并回车或直接回车</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">New</span> <span class="keyword">password</span>: &lt;– 设置root用户的密码</span><br><span class="line">Re-enter <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">password</span>: &lt;– 再输入一次你设置的密码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>其他配置</p><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Remove anonymous users? [Y/<span class="built_in">n</span>] &lt;– 是否删除匿名用户，回车</span><br><span class="line">Disallow root login remotely? [Y/<span class="built_in">n</span>] &lt;–是否禁止root远程登录,回车,</span><br><span class="line">Remove test database <span class="built_in">and</span> access to it? [Y/<span class="built_in">n</span>] &lt;– 是否删除test数据库，回车</span><br><span class="line">Reload privilege tables <span class="built_in">now</span>? [Y/<span class="built_in">n</span>] &lt;– 是否重新加载权限表，回车</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>测试登录</p><p><code> mysql -uroot -p [回车，之后输入密码] </code></p></li></ol><p>##配置MariaDB字符集</p><ol><li><p>客户端</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/my<span class="selector-class">.cnf</span><span class="selector-class">.d</span>/mysql-clients.cnf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[mysql]</span><br><span class="line">default-character-set=utf8</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>服务器</p><figure class="highlight dsconfig"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">vim </span>/<span class="string">etc/</span><span class="string">my.</span><span class="string">cnf.</span>d/<span class="string">server.</span><span class="string">cnf</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">[</span><span class="string">mysqld]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">init_connect=</span><span class="string">'SET collation_connection = utf8_general_ci'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">init_connect=</span><span class="string">'SET NAMES utf8'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">character-set-</span><span class="string">server=</span><span class="string">utf8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">collation-</span><span class="string">server=</span><span class="string">utf8_general_ci</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">skip-</span><span class="string">character-set-</span><span class="string">client-handshake</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">#</span>开启慢查询</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">slow_query_log </span>= <span class="string">ON</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">slow_query_log_file </span>= /<span class="string">usr/</span><span class="string">local/</span><span class="string">mysql/</span><span class="string">data/</span><span class="string">slow.</span><span class="string">log</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">long_query_time </span>= 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重启并查看</p><p><code> systemctl restart mariadb </code></p><p>进入数据库查看</p><p><code>  show variables like “%character%”;show variables like “%collation%”; </code></p><p>显示为</p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MariaDB [(none)]&gt; mysql&gt; show variables like "%character%";show variables like "%collation%";</span><br><span class="line">ERROR 1064 (42000): You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MariaDB server version for the right syntax to use near <span class="emphasis">'mysql&gt; show variables like "%character%"'</span> at line 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">+-------------------------------------+</span>-----------------+</span><br><span class="line">| Variable<span class="emphasis">_name                       | Value           |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">+-------------------------------------+-----------------+</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">| collation_</span>connection                | utf8<span class="emphasis">_general_</span>ci |</span><br><span class="line">| collation<span class="emphasis">_database                  | utf8_</span>general<span class="emphasis">_ci |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">| collation_</span>server                    | utf8<span class="emphasis">_general_</span>ci |</span><br><span class="line">| rocksdb<span class="emphasis">_strict_</span>collation<span class="emphasis">_check      | ON              |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">| rocksdb_</span>strict<span class="emphasis">_collation_</span>exceptions |                 |</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">+-------------------------------------+</span>-----------------+</span><br><span class="line">5 rows in set (0.01 sec)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>##添加用户，设置权限</p><ol><li><p>创建用户命令</p><p><code> CREATE USER ‘fedora‘@’%’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘fedora’; </code></p></li><li><p>创建数据库</p><p><code> create database fedora; </code></p></li><li><p>分配权限 </p><p><code> GRANT ALL ON fedora.* TO ‘fedora’ WITH GRANT OPTION; </code></p></li><li><p>外网登录</p><p><code> GRANT ALL privileges ON <em>.</em> TO fedora@’%’ identified by ‘fedora’; </code></p></li><li><p>授予权限</p><p><code> grant all privileges on <em>.</em> to fedora identified by ‘fedora’ with grant option; </code></p></li><li><p>打开防火墙</p><figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-<span class="keyword">cmd</span><span class="bash"> --add-service=http</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bash">firewall-cmd --add-service=http --permanent</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>##进入http://<em>.</em>.<em>.</em>/nextcloud进行更进一步配置</p><p> 完成后</p><p> <img src="/img/2018/04/21/Image.png" alt="Image"></p><p> [Mariadb安装之后的各种设置]： <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/zhezhebie/article/details/73549741" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/zhezhebie/article/details/73549741</a> [Fedora27installNextcloud]:<a href="https://ipsec.in/index.php/2017/11/23/fedora-27-install-nextcloud-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85nextcloud/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ipsec.in/index.php/2017/11/23/fedora-27-install-nextcloud-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85nextcloud/</a><br> [Fedora 中文用户组]: <a href="https://fzug.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://fzug.github.io/</a></p>]]></content>
    
